482
00:22:15,960 --> 00:22:18,560
What, I came here, surprised you?
-Not at all, not at all.

483
00:22:19,320 --> 00:22:21,400
This is my family, right? Watch your nonsense.

484
00:22:21,480 --> 00:22:22,840
Of course.

485
00:22:25,640 --> 00:22:28,600
By the way, did you see that woman's husband?
How gross are they?

486
00:22:28,680 --> 00:22:30,520
Sit... that woman?

487
00:22:30,600 --> 00:22:32,040
Sit!

488
00:22:38,240 --> 00:22:39,560
Oh, right, this isn't for gambling?

489
00:22:40,080 --> 00:22:42,160
So if it's not for gambling, what is it?

490
00:22:44,120 --> 00:22:45,520
What is it?

491
00:22:46,080 --> 00:22:47,320
What happened?

492
00:22:50,120 --> 00:22:51,320
What happened?

493
00:22:52,040 --> 00:22:53,600
What happened?

494
00:22:54,080 --> 00:22:56,400
What happened?
-Now it's Avi, I don't know...

495
00:22:56,480 --> 00:22:57,760
Were you even listening to me?

496
00:22:57,840 --> 00:23:00,280
Sit down, that's your name,
you're not getting that money from me,

497
00:23:00,360 --> 00:23:01,680
Are you hearing me?

